{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b420c868-e0ff-4105-b545-44393e52fee7",
    "name": "JobSearch",
    "description": "# Postman Collection Documentation - Flipris JobSearch APP\n\nUse the descriptions below to document your Postman collection. Each entry includes the **Goal**, **Headers**, and **Query Parameters** where applicable.\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 1. Auth Module\n\n### **Signup**\n\n**Goal:** Register a new user account. **Headers:** None. **Body:** `firstName`, `lastName`, `email`, `password`, `gender`, `DOB`, `mobileNumber`.\n\n### **Confirm OTP**\n\n**Goal:** Verify email address using the code sent during signup. **Headers:** None. **Body:** `email`, `otpCode`.\n\n### **SignIn**\n\n**Goal:** Authenticate user and receive Access & Refresh tokens. **Headers:** None. **Body:** `email`, `password`.\n\n### **Google Signup/Login**\n\n**Goal:** Authenticate using Google OAuth token. **Headers:** None. **Body:** `idToken`.\n\n### **Forget Password**\n\n**Goal:** Trigger a password reset OTP to be sent to the user's email. **Headers:** None. **Body:** `email`.\n\n### **Reset Password**\n\n**Goal:** Set a new password using the OTP received from \"Forget Password\". **Headers:** None. **Body:** `email`, `otpCode`, `newPassword`.\n\n### **Refresh Token**\n\n**Goal:** Obtain a new Access Token using a valid Refresh Token. **Headers:** None. **Body:** \n\nrefreshToken.\n\n### **Update Password**\n\n**Goal:** Change the password for the currently logged-in user. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `oldPassword`, `newPassword`.\n\n---\n\n## 🏢 2. Company Module\n\n### **Create Company**\n\n**Goal:** Registers a new company (Only Users can create companies). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `companyName`, `description`, `industry`, `address`, `numberOfEmployees`, `companyEmail`.\n\n### **Update Company**\n\n**Goal:** Update company details (Only Company Owner can perform this). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Path Param:** \n\nid (Company ID)\n\n### **Soft Delete Company**\n\n**Goal:** Deactivates a company (Owner/Admin only). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Path Param:** \n\nid\n\n### **Search Company**\n\n**Goal:** Find companies by name. **Query Params:** `name` (String)\n\n### **Upload Logo / Cover**\n\n**Goal:** Upload company media to Cloudinary. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `multipart/form-data` (key: `logo` or `cover`)\n\n---\n\n## 💼 3. Job Module\n\n### **Add Job**\n\n**Goal:** Post a new job opening (Owner/HR only). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `jobTitle`, `jobLocation`, `workingTime`, `seniorityLevel`, `jobDescription`, `technicalSkills`, `softSkills`.\n\n### **Get All Jobs**\n\n**Goal:** Fetch all active jobs with advanced filtering. **Query Params:**\n\n- `skip`, `limit`, `sort`\n    \n- `companyName`, `workingTime`, `jobLocation`, `seniorityLevel`, `jobTitle`, `technicalSkills`.\n    \n\n### **Get Company Jobs**\n\n**Goal:** Fetch jobs for a specific company. **Path Param:** `companyId` **Query Params:** Same as Get All Jobs.\n\n---\n\n## 📩 4. Application Module\n\n### **Apply to Job**\n\n**Goal:** Submit an application with a CV (Users only). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `multipart/form-data` (key: `cv`) **Path Param:** `jobId`\n\n### **Get Job Applications**\n\n**Goal:** View all applicants for a specific job (Owner/HR only). **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Path Param:** `jobId` **Query Params:** `skip`, `limit`.\n\n### **Update Application Status**\n\n**Goal:** Accept or Reject an application. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Body:** `status` (\"accepted\" or \"rejected\")\n\n### **Excel Export**\n\n**Goal:** Download a CSV report of applications for a specific company on a specific day. **Query Params:**\n\n- `companyId` (Required)\n    \n- date (Required, Format: YYYY-MM-DD)\n    \n\n---\n\n## 🛡️ 5. Admin Module\n\n### **Ban/Unban User or Company**\n\n**Goal:** Toggle the \"Banned\" status of a user or company. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  (Admin Only)\n\n### **GraphQL Dashboard**\n\n**Goal:** Fetch comprehensive user and company data for the admin dashboard. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  (Admin Only) **Query (GraphQL):**\n\n```\ngraphqlquery {  getDashboardData {    users { _id firstName lastName email bannedAt }    companies { _id companyName bannedAt isApproved }  }}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## 💬 6. Chat & Socket.IO\n\n### **Get Chat History**\n\n**Goal:** Fetch previous messages with a specific user. **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer`  **Path Param:** `userId` (Buddy ID)\n\n### **Real-time Chat (Socket.IO)**\n\n**Goal:** Real-time messaging between HR/Owner and Users. **Event:** \n\nsendMessage **Payload:** `{ \"receiverId\": \"ID\", \"message\": \"Hello\" }` **Listen Event:** `receiveMessage`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "47994671",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/47994671-b420c868-e0ff-4105-b545-44393e52fee7?source=collection_link"
